claim.claim-text:
A system for providing a mesh cage comprising:
a scoring device including:
a fixed body having proximal and distal ends;
a handle;
a threaded rod coupled to the handle;
first and second arms positioned at the distal end of the fixed body, the first

and second arms being moveable with respect to one another between an open condition and a closed condition; and
at least one scoring disc rotatably coupled to one of the first or second arms.
